Use this extension to have Florida Institute of CPA continuing professional education just a click away!

This powerful extension searches the FICPA's catalog and helps you stay current with the latest in the CPA world.

Questions About CPE?
If you have any questions not answered in the online catalog or in the CPE policies, please contact the FICPA Member Service Center at msc@ficpa.org. You may also call the FICPA at (800) 342-3197 or (850) 224-2727. The substitution, transfer or cancellation of a registration must be done through the Member Service Center.

*Courses listed are subject to approval by the Department of Business and Professional Regulation for both the type of credit and assigned hours.
